FT  12 DEC 92 / Finance &amp; The Family: Sterling rally peters out - At a
glance
Sterling's recent rally against the D-mark petered out this week after
Professor Wynne Godley called for a 15 per cent devaluation and 2 percentage
points off base rates. But at least, the pound has shown signs of getting
off its sickbed in December after a traumatic autumn.
